# HOW TO USE THE INSTALLER

First you need deboostrap with Ubuntu Lucid support.
On Ubuntu just install debootstrap :

sudo apt-get install debootstrap

Setup a hostname for your host, it will be used inside the subsystem.

The default will be :

hostname -f

Then run the setup script :

gitorious setup

and let :

mysql password empty
validate ruby install by pressing 'q'
and passenger by pressing enter

To change the conf of gitorious, on the host type :

gitorious conf

You need to configure on host :
gitorious init
gitorious cron
gitorious logrotate
